WEBVTT

00:17.110 --> 00:20.210
( <i>bell ringing )</i>

00:23.320 --> 00:26.830
( <i>whistle blowing )</i>

00:39.070 --> 00:41.710
( <i>playing the blues )</i>

00:58.990 --> 00:59.790
( <i>honking )</i>

01:04.230 --> 01:05.230
D-OHH!

01:05.290 --> 01:06.090
( <i>screams )</i>

01:20.280 --> 01:22.550
Would you turn off
that rock n' rock music?

01:22.610 --> 01:24.380
Hey, don't have
a stegosaurus, man.

01:24.450 --> 01:26.720
( <i>laughing )</i>

01:26.780 --> 01:28.690
THESE TALKING DINOSAURS
ARE MORE REAL

01:28.750 --> 01:30.360
THAN MOST REAL FAMILIES
ON TV.

01:30.420 --> 01:32.390
OOH! OOH! OOH..!

01:32.450 --> 01:35.580
LOOK, MAGGIE,
THEY HAVE A BABY TOO.

01:35.660 --> 01:38.930
IT'S LIKE THEY SAW OUR LIVES
AND PUT IT RIGHT UP ON SCREEN.

01:38.990 --> 01:41.120
NOW KIDS, I KNOW
YOU'RE ALL EXCITED

01:41.200 --> 01:43.270
ABOUT MEETING AUNT SELMA'S
NEW BOYFRIEND TONIGHT.

01:43.330 --> 01:43.940
( <i>raspberry )</i>

01:44.000 --> 01:44.640
BUT I THINK THAT

01:44.700 --> 01:45.770
BEFORE HE GETS HERE

01:45.830 --> 01:47.500
I SHOULD TELL YOU
SOMETHING ABOUT HIM--

01:47.570 --> 01:49.470
SOMETHING <i>DISTURBING.</i>

01:50.640 --> 01:52.310
OOH!

01:52.370 --> 01:54.070
OOH!

01:54.140 --> 01:56.000
EYUGH!

01:56.080 --> 01:58.750
YOU SEE, AUNT SELMA HAS
THIS CRAZY OBSESSION

01:58.810 --> 02:00.040
ABOUT NOT DYING ALONE.

02:00.120 --> 02:01.550
SO IN DESPERATION

02:01.620 --> 02:04.060
SHE JOINED THIS PRISON
PEN PAL PROGRAM.

02:04.120 --> 02:06.060
HER NEW SWEETIE
IS A JAILBIRD.

02:06.120 --> 02:07.960
<i>COOL, HE CAN TEACH US</i>

02:08.020 --> 02:09.780
HOW TO KILL A MAN
WITH A LUNCH TRAY.

02:09.860 --> 02:13.230
NOW, NOW, HE'S
AN <i>EX-CONVICT.</i>

02:13.300 --> 02:15.030
HE'S PAID HIS DEBT
TO SOCIETY.

02:15.100 --> 02:16.500
THEN HOW COME
YOU'RE NOT USING

02:16.570 --> 02:18.100
THE GOOD SILVERWARE?

02:18.170 --> 02:19.070
I'M JUST NOT.

02:19.130 --> 02:19.930
( <i>doorbell )</i>

02:20.000 --> 02:20.770
THAT'S THEM.

02:20.840 --> 02:22.410
REMEMBER, EVERYONE

02:22.470 --> 02:24.710
BE UNDERSTANDING
AND FORGIVING

02:24.770 --> 02:26.170
FOR THE SAKE
OF FAMILY UNITY.

02:27.680 --> 02:29.950
EVERYONE
I'D LIKE YOU TO MEET...

02:30.010 --> 02:31.920
AAH! SIDESHOW BOB!

02:31.980 --> 02:33.420
Selma:
WHAT THE..?

02:33.480 --> 02:34.750
SELMA, DEAR, I'M AFRAID
THE CHILDREN'S REACTION

02:34.820 --> 02:36.450
IS QUITE UNDERSTANDABLE.

02:36.520 --> 02:38.160
YOU SEE, BART HERE
IS THE SHAMUS
IN SHORT PANTS

02:38.220 --> 02:39.260
WHO SENT ME
TO PRISON.

02:39.320 --> 02:40.690
THAT'S RIGHT, AUNT SELMA.

02:40.760 --> 02:42.930
YOUR NEW BOYFRIEND HERE
FRAMED KRUSTY THE CLOWN

02:42.990 --> 02:44.260
FOR ARMED ROBBERY.

02:44.330 --> 02:45.800
( <i>gasp )</i>

02:45.860 --> 02:48.500
GEE, IF SOME SNOT-NOSED
LITTLE KID SENT ME TO PRISON,

02:48.560 --> 02:50.860
THE FIRST THING OUT
I'D FIND OUT WHERE HE LIVES

02:50.930 --> 02:53.130
AND TEAR HIM
A NEW BELLY-BUTTON.

02:53.200 --> 02:55.040
( <i>grunts )</i>

02:55.100 --> 02:56.460
LOUSY SNITCH.

02:56.540 --> 02:57.440
<i>YAAH!</i>

02:57.510 --> 02:59.780
( <i>nervous laughter )</i>

02:59.840 --> 03:01.380
AH, MR. SIMPSON.

03:01.440 --> 03:03.400
YOU'RE FORGETTING
THE FIRST TWO NOBLE TRUTHS

03:03.480 --> 03:04.250
OF THE BUDDHA.

03:04.310 --> 03:04.940
I AM NOT.

03:05.010 --> 03:06.070
YES, YOU ARE.

03:06.150 --> 03:08.590
ONE:
EXISTENCE IS SUFFERING.

03:08.650 --> 03:11.790
TWO: THE CAUSE
OF SUFFERING IS DESIRE--

03:11.850 --> 03:14.080
IN THIS CASE, MY DESIRE
TO DO HIGH-QUALITY

03:14.160 --> 03:15.130
CHILDREN'S PROGRAMMING.

03:17.090 --> 03:18.250
<i>WHEN PRISON PUT AN END
TO THAT DREAM,</i>

03:18.330 --> 03:19.800
<i>I BECAME A SEETHING CAULDRON</i>

03:19.860 --> 03:21.200
<i>OF RAGE AND RECRIMINATION.</i>

03:38.350 --> 03:39.420
<i>WHEN I WAS NOMINATED</i>

03:39.480 --> 03:41.120
<i>FOR BEST SUPPORTING PERFORMER</i>

03:41.180 --> 03:42.180
<i>IN A CHILDREN'S PROGRAM</i>

03:42.250 --> 03:43.490
<i>AT THE DAYTIME EMMY AWARDS,</i>

03:43.550 --> 03:45.390
<i>MY BITTERNESS RUINED</i>

03:45.450 --> 03:47.520
<i>WHAT SHOULD HAVE BEEN
THE GREATEST NIGHT OF MY LIFE.</i>

03:47.590 --> 03:48.730
AND THE NOMINEES ARE:

03:48.790 --> 03:50.300
DROOPY DRAWERS,

03:50.360 --> 03:51.730
COLONEL COWARD,

03:51.790 --> 03:54.960
PEPITO, THE BIGGEST CAT
IN THE WHOLE WIDE WORLD,

03:55.030 --> 03:57.170
SIDESHOW BOB,

03:57.230 --> 03:59.260
AND SUCKUP THE VACUUM.

03:59.330 --> 04:01.600
AND THE EMMY GOES TO...

04:01.670 --> 04:03.310
I DON'T BELIEVE THIS...

04:03.370 --> 04:05.280
SIDESHOW BOB.

04:05.340 --> 04:07.350
<i>( applause )</i>

04:09.140 --> 04:10.970
THIS IS ONE MORE EMMY
THAN YOU'LL EVER WIN

04:11.050 --> 04:13.250
YOU BANTERING JACK-IN-THE-BOX!

04:13.320 --> 04:15.350
JUST DON'T DROP THAT THING
IN THE SHOWER, BOB.

04:15.420 --> 04:16.820
NO-TALENT, SHILL!
SECOND BANANA!

04:16.890 --> 04:17.860
PANDERER!
BORE!

04:17.920 --> 04:19.620
( <i>muffled protests )</i>

04:23.090 --> 04:25.530
UH, NOW FOR THE HIGHLIGHT
OF THE EVENING--

04:25.590 --> 04:27.020
BEST FILM-TO-VIDEO TRANSFER.

04:28.460 --> 04:29.960
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT PRISON IS LIKE

04:30.030 --> 04:31.900
FOR A LIFE-LONG,
CONSERVATIVE REPUBLICAN?

04:35.870 --> 04:37.240
<i>IN OUR OVERCROWDED CELL</i>

04:37.310 --> 04:39.480
<i>WE BECAME LITTLE MORE
THAN BEASTS.</i>

04:39.540 --> 04:40.880
WHO USED MY CHAP STICK?

04:40.940 --> 04:41.670
OH, I DID.

04:41.740 --> 04:42.670
HERE YOU GO.

04:42.740 --> 04:44.310
I DON'T WANT IT.

04:44.380 --> 04:47.590
<i>MY ONLY JOY CAME WITH PLOTTING
A HORRIBLE REVENGE</i>

04:47.650 --> 04:49.090
<i>AGAINST THE BOY
WHO PUT ME THERE.</i>

04:56.630 --> 04:58.000
<i>AY, CARAMBA!</i>

04:58.060 --> 04:59.500
BART, IF I
WANTED TO KILL YOU

04:59.560 --> 05:01.100
I'D HAVE CHOKED YOU
LIKE A CHICKEN

05:01.160 --> 05:02.320
AS SOON AS I WALKED IN
THAT DOOR.

05:02.400 --> 05:03.400
( <i>gasps )</i>

05:03.470 --> 05:04.340
BUT THEN WHAT KIND
OF A GUEST

05:04.400 --> 05:05.340
WOULD I HAVE BEEN?

05:05.400 --> 05:08.610
( <i>laughter )</i>

05:08.670 --> 05:09.970
NOW, WHERE WAS I?

05:10.040 --> 05:12.910
AH, YES-- MY LOWEST EBB.

05:12.980 --> 05:14.950
YOU CAN'T TAKE
MY EMMY.

05:15.010 --> 05:16.610
YOU KNOW THE RULES:

05:16.680 --> 05:19.080
AWARDS FOR EXCELLENCE
IN ENTERTAINMENT
ARE CONTRABAND.

05:19.150 --> 05:20.220
NO EMMYS, NO OSCARS,

05:20.280 --> 05:21.420
NOT EVEN
A GOLDEN GLOBE.

05:23.750 --> 05:26.650
BUT KISMET CAN BE KIND,
AS WELL AS CRUEL.

05:26.720 --> 05:28.090
<i>I RECEIVED AN ANSWER
TO MY LETTER</i>

05:28.160 --> 05:29.730
<i>FROM THE PRISON
PEN PAL PROGRAM.</i>

05:29.790 --> 05:33.030
Selma:
<i>"DEAR #24601...</i>

05:33.100 --> 05:35.570
<i>"I NEED A MAN
AND I CANNOT FIND ONE</i>

05:35.630 --> 05:37.270
<i>"AMONG THE LAW ABIDING.</i>

05:37.330 --> 05:40.090
<i>"I HAVE A STEADY JOB
AND A LUCRATIVE HOBBY:</i>

05:40.170 --> 05:42.140
<i>"FILING NUISANCE LAWSUITS.</i>

05:42.200 --> 05:44.130
<i>"I SHARE AN APARTMENT
WITH MY TWIN SISTER.</i>

05:44.210 --> 05:45.710
<i>"ENCLOSED IS A PHOTO OF US</i>

05:45.770 --> 05:46.970
<i>"ON A TANDEM BIKE.</i>

05:47.040 --> 05:48.380
<i>I FORGET WHICH ONE I AM."</i>

05:50.350 --> 05:51.450
Bob:
<i>"DEAR SELMA...</i>

05:51.510 --> 05:53.570
<i>"YOUR LATEST LETTER
SET OFF A RIOT</i>

05:53.650 --> 05:56.390
<i>IN THE MAXIMUM-SECURITY WING
OF MY HEART."</i>

05:56.450 --> 05:59.220
OHHH...

05:59.290 --> 06:00.760
( <i>pffft )</i>

06:00.820 --> 06:03.790
<i>LIKE THE LONE CROCUS THAT POKES
THROUGH THE PRISON YARD</i>

06:03.860 --> 06:06.060
<i>OUR LOVE BLOOMED
DESPITE ALL OBSTACLES.</i>

06:08.330 --> 06:10.230
SELMA, MAY I?

06:10.300 --> 06:11.700
UH, UH, UH...

06:11.770 --> 06:14.240
ON THE CHEEK.

06:14.300 --> 06:15.260
( <i>kissing )</i>

06:17.140 --> 06:18.880
<i>INSPIRED BY THE LOVE
OF A GOOD WOMAN</i>

06:18.940 --> 06:20.380
<i>I RESOLVED TO BE</i>

06:20.440 --> 06:22.300
<i>THE BEST DARNED INMATE
#24601 I COULD BE.</i>

06:25.680 --> 06:27.520
<i>I BADE FAREWELL TO MY CELLMATES</i>

06:27.580 --> 06:28.880
<i>AND LEFT WITH THE WOMAN
I LOVED.</i>

06:30.190 --> 06:31.390
CUTTER...

06:31.450 --> 06:33.280
ICEPICK...

06:33.360 --> 06:34.430
SNAKE...

06:34.490 --> 06:36.160
I'M GOING TO MISS YOU
MOST OF ALL.

06:38.230 --> 06:40.000
All:
AWW!

06:40.060 --> 06:42.170
WHAT A BEAUTIFUL STORY,
SIDESHOW BOB.

06:42.230 --> 06:43.370
YOU'RE LIVING PROOF

06:43.430 --> 06:45.670
THAT OUR REVOLVING-DOOR
PRISON SYSTEM WORKS.

06:45.730 --> 06:47.830
SELMA, I'VE NEVER
SEEN YOU SO HAPPY--

06:47.900 --> 06:49.660
GIGGLING LIKE A SCHOOLGIRL.

06:49.740 --> 06:52.710
( <i>hoarse giggles )</i>

06:52.770 --> 06:54.640
I'VE GOT TO ADMIT IT,
SELMA

06:54.710 --> 06:56.680
HE'S A ONCE-IN-A-LIFETIME
CATCH.

06:56.750 --> 06:59.650
YES, I HOPE THE POLICE
ARE SAYING THAT AS WELL.

06:59.720 --> 07:01.990
( <i>laughing )</i>

07:03.250 --> 07:04.720
I CAN'T BELIEVE YOU GUYS.

07:04.790 --> 07:06.820
THIS MAN FRAMED
KRUSTY THE CLOWN.

07:06.890 --> 07:07.590
BART!

07:07.660 --> 07:09.030
INDEED, I DID

07:09.090 --> 07:12.200
AND I'D LIKE TO THANK YOU
FOR CATCHING ME, BART.

07:12.260 --> 07:13.300
YOU SEIZED THE WHEEL

07:13.360 --> 07:15.100
OF MY SLOW BOAT TO HELL,
AND POINTED IT

07:15.160 --> 07:17.760
STRAIGHT TOWARDS
THE SUNNY SHORES OF SELMA.

07:17.830 --> 07:18.830
HERE, HERE.

07:18.900 --> 07:20.740
SELMA, WOULD YOU MIND

07:20.800 --> 07:22.830
IF I DID SOMETHING
BOLD AND SHOCKING

07:22.900 --> 07:23.870
IN FRONT OF YOUR FAMILY?

07:23.940 --> 07:25.340
ALL RIGHT,
BUT NO TONGUES.

07:25.410 --> 07:26.510
ALTHOUGH KISSING YOU

07:26.580 --> 07:28.650
WOULD BE LIKE KISSING
SOME DIVINE ASHTRAY,

07:28.710 --> 07:29.950
THAT'S NOT WHAT
I HAD IN MIND.

07:30.010 --> 07:33.320
SELMA, WILL YOU MARRY ME?

07:33.380 --> 07:34.320
( <i>gasps )</i>

07:34.380 --> 07:35.610
DON'T BE A FOOL,
AUNT SELMA.

07:35.680 --> 07:36.840
THAT MAN IS SCUM.

07:36.920 --> 07:39.290
THEN CALL ME "MRS. SCUM."

